00:29:11,680 --> 00:29:12,600
How old are you?

570
00:29:14,530 --> 00:29:15,120
42.

571
00:29:15,520 --> 00:29:16,320
What's wrong?

572
00:29:16,360 --> 00:29:18,830
What were you doing at 28 or 29?

573
00:29:19,930 --> 00:29:22,390
I was a secretary at a public institute at 28.

574
00:29:23,430 --> 00:29:25,590
I ran errands for the boss at work,

575
00:29:26,170 --> 00:29:27,880
and went to the gym after work.

576
00:29:28,850 --> 00:29:30,930
Then I went home and felt lost.

577
00:29:31,370 --> 00:29:33,570
I was searching for the meaning of life.

578
00:29:36,080 --> 00:29:37,200
Why do you ask?

579
00:29:41,210 --> 00:29:44,170
I think what you said was right.

580
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:49,350
Sometimes we should slow down a young person's career progress.

581
00:30:03,510 --> 00:30:04,150
Yingzi?

582
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:06,930
Mr. Zhou, sorry to trouble you again.

583
00:30:07,130 --> 00:30:09,370
I was in the court the whole time.

584
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,460
I'm sorry for what you've been through.

585
00:30:11,460 --> 00:30:13,210
You shouldn't have been dragged into this.

586
00:30:13,210 --> 00:30:14,120
It's unfair.

587
00:30:14,210 --> 00:30:17,320
Mr. Zhou, I'm here to ask for your help.

588
00:30:17,410 --> 00:30:19,360
Can you invite the four creditors

589
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:21,120
to a meeting with me?

590
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:23,330
I want to talk to them

591
00:30:23,330 --> 00:30:24,290
about how to repay the debts.

592
00:30:24,290 --> 00:30:27,160
Could you be a mediator?

593
00:30:27,890 --> 00:30:29,170
I'll gather them.

594
00:30:29,170 --> 00:30:30,040
That's easy.

595
00:30:30,120 --> 00:30:31,120
When do you want to see them?

596
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:32,160
Please just gather them.

597
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,570
When it's done, tell me about it.

598
00:30:33,570 --> 00:30:34,810
I'm available anytime.

599
00:30:34,810 --> 00:30:35,500
Piece of cake.

600
00:30:35,500 --> 00:30:36,930
-Thank you.
-I'll take you out to eat.

601
00:30:36,930 --> 00:30:37,570
No, no, no.

602
00:30:37,570 --> 00:30:38,680
-It's time to eat.
-Mr. Zhou.

603
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:39,890
Let's go.
-I'm sorry to bother you.

604
00:30:39,890 --> 00:30:41,570
I shouldn't take up any more of your time.

605
00:30:41,570 --> 00:30:42,520
I should probably get going.

606
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:44,450
You've done this several times...

607
00:30:48,130 --> 00:30:48,760
Yingzi,

608
00:30:49,810 --> 00:30:51,150
I have an idea.

609
00:30:52,090 --> 00:30:53,130
Be my girl,

610
00:30:53,450 --> 00:30:54,970
and I'll pay all your debts.

611
00:30:54,970 --> 00:30:56,530
It's gonna make your life much easier.

612
00:30:56,530 --> 00:30:57,570
No, Mr. Zhou, I...

613
00:30:58,080 --> 00:30:59,320
I don't know what you're talking about.

614
00:30:59,320 --> 00:31:00,650
I... I should really go.

615
00:31:02,280 --> 00:31:03,920
What's wrong with you?

616
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:07,280
Is this what you want as a reward?

617
00:31:08,410 --> 00:31:09,360
I've let you call me "Yingzi".

618
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,420
Isn't that enough?

619
00:31:11,120 --> 00:31:12,890
Should I tell my dad about this?

620
00:31:13,050 --> 00:31:14,580
Then he'll tell your uncle.

621
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:17,890
Are you out of your mind?

622
00:31:18,840 --> 00:31:20,170
Well...

623
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:21,600
I was just kidding.

624
00:31:21,600 --> 00:31:22,600
It was a joke.

625
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:23,330
I didn't mean it.

626
00:31:23,330 --> 00:31:25,530
How was I supposed to know that's a joke?

627
00:31:25,760 --> 00:31:27,170
You scared me!

628
00:31:27,570 --> 00:31:29,120
Don't forget what I asked you for!

629
00:31:29,120 --> 00:31:29,960
Yingzi, wait!

630
00:31:43,840 --> 00:31:44,530
Yingzi,

631
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:46,330
why does Mr. Zhou

632
00:31:46,370 --> 00:31:47,530
give us so much help?

633
00:31:49,250 --> 00:31:50,780
Mr. Zhou

634
00:31:51,290 --> 00:31:52,610
loves to help.

635
00:31:53,050 --> 00:31:54,110
I don't believe it.

636
00:31:54,560 --> 00:31:56,020
He must be up to something.

637
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:58,240
He helped us when we sold the apartment.

638
00:31:58,540 --> 00:32:00,170
If he can't get any benefits this time,

639
00:32:00,170 --> 00:32:01,630
why would he help us again?

640
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,890
What do you think the reason is?

641
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:05,570
Lanlan,

642
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:08,460
the relationship between people

643
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,520
is not just about interests.

644
00:32:12,190 --> 00:32:13,520
Take you for an example.

645
00:32:14,450 --> 00:32:15,280
You're at my place,

646
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:17,100
and you make less money than before.

647
00:32:17,100 --> 00:32:19,140
Why do you still choose to stay?

648
00:32:20,740 --> 00:32:21,870
That's a good point.

649
00:32:22,850 --> 00:32:23,310
Yingzi,

650
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:24,970
I think,

651
00:32:25,130 --> 00:32:26,120
no matter what,

652
00:32:26,690 --> 00:32:28,840
we've gotta thank Mr. Zhou.

653
00:32:30,320 --> 00:32:32,160
It's too huge a favor.

654
00:32:32,790 --> 00:32:34,110
How is it possible

655
00:32:34,610 --> 00:32:36,010
for me to ever pay it back?

656
00:32:37,770 --> 00:32:39,380
[Zhou Houze]

657
00:32:38,720 --> 00:32:39,320
Yingzi,

658
00:32:39,760 --> 00:32:40,560
it's Mr. Zhou.

659
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:52,010
Hello.

660
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:53,690
Mr. Zhou.

661
00:32:55,060 --> 00:32:55,590
What?

662
00:32:56,650 --> 00:32:57,330
Okay.

663
00:32:59,050 --> 00:32:59,960
When?

664
00:33:01,460 --> 00:33:03,810
10 a.m. tomorrow.

665
00:33:04,430 --> 00:33:04,990
Okay.

666
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:07,000
I'll be there on time.

667
00:33:08,520 --> 00:33:09,130
Okay.

668
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:11,240
Thank you, Mr. Zhou.

669
00:33:11,650 --> 00:33:12,210
Bye.

670
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:14,370
What is it?

671
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:17,360
I asked him to gather the creditors for me.

672
00:33:17,930 --> 00:33:18,600
He did it.

673
00:33:18,620 --> 00:33:20,950
The meeting's set to take place tomorrow.

674
00:33:22,090 --> 00:33:22,640
Yingzi,

675
00:33:23,330 --> 00:33:25,160
he cares about you so much.

676
00:33:27,310 --> 00:33:28,640
I begged him for a favor.

677
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:30,040
Is he into you?

678
00:33:32,770 --> 00:33:34,570
Lanlan, stop talking nonsense.

679
00:33:36,850 --> 00:33:38,310
I don't think he's into me.

680
00:33:38,890 --> 00:33:40,920
He's not my cup of tea.

681
00:33:41,610 --> 00:33:42,930
I treat him as a friend.

682
00:33:42,930 --> 00:33:44,770
Yingzi, look at him,

683
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:46,680
capable and rich.

684
00:33:46,850 --> 00:33:48,570
Dating him

685
00:33:48,610 --> 00:33:49,890
wouldn't be a bad thing.

686
00:33:49,890 --> 00:33:51,930
Lanlan, stop it or I'll be mad at you.

687
00:33:52,610 --> 00:33:54,610
What kind of person do you think I am?

688
00:34:07,410 --> 00:34:08,580
Lanlan, I'm going out.

689
00:34:08,580 --> 00:34:10,210
I may not be able to come back for lunch.

690
00:34:10,210 --> 00:34:11,000
Don't wait for me.

691
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:11,530
Yingzi,

692
00:34:11,929 --> 00:34:12,860
I'll go with you.

693
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:14,650
Why?

694
00:34:15,010 --> 00:34:15,929
It's a big deal.

695
00:34:15,929 --> 00:34:17,770
I must go with you or I'll be very worried.

696
00:34:17,770 --> 00:34:18,560
It's my own business.

697
00:34:18,560 --> 00:34:19,560
I can do it myself.

698
00:34:19,690 --> 00:34:20,370
Yingzi,

699
00:34:20,730 --> 00:34:22,080
I treat you as my own sister,

700
00:34:22,080 --> 00:34:23,320
but you see me as a stranger.

701
00:34:23,320 --> 00:34:25,230
That's what I fear you'd say.

702
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:26,030
Alright, let's go.

703
00:34:26,030 --> 00:34:27,219
Let's go.

704
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:30,520
These gentlemen

705
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,880
have been friends with me for years.

706
00:34:32,929 --> 00:34:34,790
Guys, she's a dear friend of mine.

707
00:34:35,360 --> 00:34:37,090
We should treat the people here

708
00:34:37,290 --> 00:34:38,170
as family.

709
00:34:38,770 --> 00:34:40,360
If you have something to say,

710
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,199
say it nicely.

711
00:34:41,219 --> 00:34:42,440
We'll have a friendly talk.

712
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:42,969
Okay.

713
00:34:44,690 --> 00:34:45,199
Yingzi,

714
00:34:45,530 --> 00:34:46,330
you go first.

715
00:34:46,530 --> 00:34:47,010
Okay.

716
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:47,639
Thank you.

717
00:34:50,239 --> 00:34:51,010
Gentlemen,

718
00:34:52,489 --> 00:34:53,750
let me make this clear:

719
00:34:56,050 --> 00:34:56,960
I won't deny

720
00:34:57,970 --> 00:34:58,770
the debts.

721
00:34:59,450 --> 00:35:01,770
You must have seen

722
00:35:01,770 --> 00:35:03,700
the evidence I exhibited in court.

723
00:35:04,090 --> 00:35:05,400
All my money at home

724
00:35:06,570 --> 00:35:07,770
has been transferred

725
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:09,360
by my husband.

726
00:35:09,890 --> 00:35:11,650
I was set up by him.

727
00:35:12,490 --> 00:35:13,850
The debts you're trying to collect

728
00:35:13,850 --> 00:35:16,080
actually have nothing to do with me.

729
00:35:16,370 --> 00:35:17,090
Ms. Luo,

730
00:35:17,850 --> 00:35:20,080
what your husband did to you doesn't concern us.

731
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:21,320
Sir, calm down.

732
00:35:21,930 --> 00:35:23,170
Let me finish.

733
00:35:24,370 --> 00:35:26,360
I have a car under my name.

734
00:35:26,600 --> 00:35:27,840
The car under my husband's name

735
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:29,160
is also in the country.

736
00:35:31,040 --> 00:35:31,680
However,

737
00:35:32,040 --> 00:35:34,360
my house has been taken away by the bank.

738
00:35:34,930 --> 00:35:37,690
I'll sell these two cars as soon as possible

739
00:35:38,080 --> 00:35:40,360
and get some money from my parents.

740
00:35:40,880 --> 00:35:42,410
I'm doing everything I can.

741
00:35:45,890 --> 00:35:46,620
To be honest,

742
00:35:46,760 --> 00:35:47,890
no matter how hard I try,

743
00:35:47,890 --> 00:35:50,220
it's still not enough to pay all the debts.

744
00:35:50,290 --> 00:35:51,530
I have an idea.

745
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:54,250
I'll pay 70% of the total amount

746
00:35:54,290 --> 00:35:55,610
all at once.

747
00:35:55,970 --> 00:35:57,680
Then we'll call it even.

748
00:35:58,210 --> 00:36:00,140
The whole thing will come to an end.

749
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:02,130
Here's a further explanation.

750
00:36:02,450 --> 00:36:04,760
Plus the interest my husband paid before,

751
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:06,450
and the 70% of the debts I'm gonna repay,

752
00:36:06,450 --> 00:36:08,730
you'll yield a big enough profit.

753
00:36:09,370 --> 00:36:11,170
If you agree with what I suggest,

754
00:36:11,290 --> 00:36:12,820
I'll do as I said right away.

755
00:36:13,280 --> 00:36:14,760
If you don't agree,

756
00:36:16,090 --> 00:36:17,730
I'll have to

757
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:19,210
to fight you in court.

758
00:36:19,890 --> 00:36:21,440
I'm afraid that the longer the process is,

759
00:36:21,440 --> 00:36:22,900
the less money I will have.

760
00:36:23,160 --> 00:36:24,200
In the end,

761
00:36:25,410 --> 00:36:27,740
you won't be able to take anything from me,

762
00:36:27,860 --> 00:36:29,060
except for my life.

763
00:36:32,520 --> 00:36:34,520
Gentlemen, there's one more thing.

764
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:35,920
The money her husband borrowed

765
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:38,390
wasn't used for their marriage life.

766
00:36:38,570 --> 00:36:40,300
We have evidence to prove that.

767
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:43,200
Yingzi is willing to pay what Liu Ming owes.

768
00:36:43,430 --> 00:36:45,340
But other than the principal of the loans,

769
00:36:45,340 --> 00:36:47,570
she could only afford a small extra amount.

770
00:36:47,570 --> 00:36:48,450
We're here today

771
00:36:48,450 --> 00:36:50,000
to discuss with you

772
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:51,720
through peaceful dialogue.

773
00:36:53,090 --> 00:36:54,370
If you

774
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:55,570
don't agree,

775
00:36:55,570 --> 00:36:57,770
we'll wait for the court to rule on this.

776
00:36:59,410 --> 00:37:00,460
I disagree.

777
00:37:01,890 --> 00:37:03,820
Ms. Qiu, I don't like what you said.

778
00:37:05,440 --> 00:37:06,080
Yingzi,

779
00:37:06,750 --> 00:37:08,350
don't take that tone with us.

780
00:37:09,180 --> 00:37:11,350
Forget about the lawsuits,

781
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:13,260
and those negative remarks.

782
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,930
What kind of attitude is that?

783
00:37:14,930 --> 00:37:16,080
In all fairness,

784
00:37:16,890 --> 00:37:17,890
My buddies

785
00:37:18,160 --> 00:37:19,240
make a living by

786
00:37:19,280 --> 00:37:20,720
lending you money and taking it back

787
00:37:20,720 --> 00:37:22,120
with interest attached.

788
00:37:22,230 --> 00:37:24,490
Without it, their business will strand.

789
00:37:24,570 --> 00:37:25,050
Yingzi,

790
00:37:26,290 --> 00:37:28,720
apart from meeting your basic living needs,

791
00:37:28,720 --> 00:37:29,560
you should use the rest of your money

792
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:30,620
to repay the debts.

793
00:37:32,850 --> 00:37:33,490
Guys,

794
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:35,610
listen,

795
00:37:35,640 --> 00:37:37,010
on behalf of Yingzi,

796
00:37:37,010 --> 00:37:38,740
I've gotta tell you something.

797
00:37:39,930 --> 00:37:40,790
She

798
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:43,120
married to a wrong guy.

799
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:45,280
Her apartment

800
00:37:45,310 --> 00:37:46,760
was confiscated by the court.

801
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:48,160
The two ruddy cars she has

802
00:37:48,370 --> 00:37:50,230
will be sold soon to pay the debts.

803
00:37:50,250 --> 00:37:51,580
Indeed, she's a lawyer,

804
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:53,010
but now she just works as

805
00:37:53,010 --> 00:37:54,160
an underpaid pupil.

806
00:37:56,370 --> 00:37:57,080
Guys,

807
00:37:58,410 --> 00:37:59,270
how about this?

808
00:38:00,370 --> 00:38:02,030
Do me a favor and cut her loose.

809
00:38:03,490 --> 00:38:04,090
Guys.

810
00:38:04,810 --> 00:38:05,450
Shall we

811
00:38:06,210 --> 00:38:06,890
settle?

812
00:38:07,690 --> 00:38:09,150
The worst part is that Mr. Zhou backs her up.

813
00:38:09,150 --> 00:38:10,120
We can't do anything.

814
00:38:10,120 --> 00:38:12,720
Yingzi, they're discussing. It's a good sign.

815
00:38:15,350 --> 00:38:16,320
Mr. Zhou,

816
00:38:16,730 --> 00:38:18,390
thank you for helping Yingzi.

817
00:38:18,410 --> 00:38:19,890
I'd like to propose a toast to you.

818
00:38:19,890 --> 00:38:21,550
Does she work in your law firm?

819
00:38:21,730 --> 00:38:23,930
Lanlan is currently working at my home.

820
00:38:25,140 --> 00:38:26,700
She's a nanny then.

821
00:38:26,720 --> 00:38:27,440
Mr. Zhou.

822
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:28,890
It's okay, Yingzi.

823
00:38:28,890 --> 00:38:29,680
Mr. Zhou,

824
00:38:29,720 --> 00:38:31,090
I'm not a nanny.

825
00:38:31,210 --> 00:38:33,340
I'm not staying with Yingzi for money.

826
00:38:33,440 --> 00:38:35,360
I'm studying law with her.

827
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:37,220
I want to be a lawyer in the future.

828
00:38:38,530 --> 00:38:39,160
Good.

829
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:41,010
-Cheers!
-Ambitious girl!

830
00:38:41,050 --> 00:38:41,440
Okay.

831
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:51,450
Guys,

832
00:38:51,710 --> 00:38:53,170
how did the discussion go?

833
00:39:00,810 --> 00:39:02,010
We've got a decision.

834
00:39:02,770 --> 00:39:03,370
Ms. Luo,

835
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:04,520
you'll pay 80% of the total amount

836
00:39:04,520 --> 00:39:06,760
in proper proportion.

837
00:39:07,370 --> 00:39:09,560
Gentlemen, I really can't afford that much.

838
00:39:09,560 --> 00:39:10,050
Yingzi,

839
00:39:11,190 --> 00:39:12,370
take it as a win.

840
00:39:22,260 --> 00:39:23,120
How about this?

841
00:39:23,690 --> 00:39:25,420
You give them as much money as you can.

842
00:39:25,420 --> 00:39:26,750
I'll deal with the rest.

843
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:27,330
Mr. Zhou,

844
00:39:28,040 --> 00:39:29,560
we can't let you do this.

845
00:39:29,940 --> 00:39:31,040
How can we take your money?

846
00:39:31,040 --> 00:39:31,530
What do you mean?

847
00:39:31,530 --> 00:39:32,210
This is it.

848
00:39:32,230 --> 00:39:33,090
It's a deal now.

849
00:39:33,520 --> 00:39:34,690
By only asking for 80% of the debts,

850
00:39:34,690 --> 00:39:35,930
you've shown me enough respect.

851
00:39:35,930 --> 00:39:37,260
Let's put an end to this.

852
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:41,580
As we said before,

853
00:39:41,600 --> 00:39:42,960
I'll pay you 80% of the debts,

854
00:39:42,960 --> 00:39:44,640
and we'll be even. Right?

855
00:39:44,930 --> 00:39:45,460
We agree.

856
00:39:45,720 --> 00:39:46,960
When she pays us 80% of the total amount,

857
00:39:46,960 --> 00:39:48,460
we'll consider the whole thing over.

858
00:39:48,460 --> 00:39:49,300
Okay.

859
00:39:50,020 --> 00:39:52,020
We've prepared 4 contracts.

860
00:39:52,370 --> 00:39:53,720
Let's calculate

861
00:39:53,740 --> 00:39:54,870
the proportion.

862
00:39:55,320 --> 00:39:55,970
Alright.

863
00:39:56,240 --> 00:39:57,680
We'll do it later.

864
00:39:58,010 --> 00:39:59,090
What's the rush for?

865
00:39:59,090 --> 00:40:00,660
Come, sit down.

866
00:40:00,690 --> 00:40:01,640
What a successful result!

867
00:40:01,640 --> 00:40:03,080
Let's drink!

868
00:40:06,720 --> 00:40:07,800
Let me walk you out.

869
00:40:08,530 --> 00:40:09,460
Come on, Yingzi.

870
00:40:12,640 --> 00:40:14,710
Did you ask the bank to take the apartment?

871
00:40:14,710 --> 00:40:15,670
No.

872
00:40:15,960 --> 00:40:16,870
I'm serious.

873
00:40:16,920 --> 00:40:18,740
A few days ago, I was homeless.

874
00:40:19,890 --> 00:40:20,930
I understand.

875
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:22,650
The bank has taken the apartment.

876
00:40:22,650 --> 00:40:24,110
You can get it back through a trial.

877
00:40:24,110 --> 00:40:25,210
If it falls into my friends' hands,

878
00:40:25,210 --> 00:40:26,280
it'll be as good as gone.

879
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:26,810
Mr. Zhou,

880
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,160
please stop here.

881
00:40:28,320 --> 00:40:30,090
I owe you so many thanks.

882
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,290
Thank you, Mr. Zhou.

883
00:40:31,290 --> 00:40:32,160
No worries.

884
00:40:32,210 --> 00:40:33,190
I'll go back and drink with them.

885
00:40:33,190 --> 00:40:33,530
Okay.

886
00:40:34,280 --> 00:40:34,910
Thank you.

887
00:40:42,110 --> 00:40:42,640
Yingzi,

888
00:40:42,770 --> 00:40:44,680
you're going back to the law firm but I'm not.

889
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:45,970
I saw a supermarket nearby.

890
00:40:45,970 --> 00:40:48,300
I wanna go and buy some meat and vegetable.

891
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,370
Don't we have any of that at home?

892
00:40:49,370 --> 00:40:50,090
No.

893
00:40:51,570 --> 00:40:52,330
You can go.

894
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:54,040
Don't buy too much.

895
00:40:54,530 --> 00:40:55,930
Every time you bought too much, some of it rotted.

896
00:40:55,930 --> 00:40:56,890
I'll bear that in mind.

897
00:40:56,890 --> 00:40:57,850
Drive safe.

898
00:40:57,890 --> 00:40:58,370
Okay.

899
00:40:58,370 --> 00:40:59,170
I'm leaving.

900
00:41:04,100 --> 00:41:06,300
Do you have problems getting the money?

901
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:08,840
I can deal with it.

902
00:41:11,280 --> 00:41:11,980
Qiu Hua,

903
00:41:13,510 --> 00:41:15,650
did you tell the bank

904
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,360
that Liu Ming ran away?

905
00:41:19,450 --> 00:41:20,140
Sorry.

906
00:41:20,170 --> 00:41:21,830
I didn't tell you beforehead.

907
00:41:21,850 --> 00:41:22,760
Technically speaking,

908
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:25,010
it's against a lawyer's professional ethic.

909
00:41:25,010 --> 00:41:27,140
But another I knew was more important.

910
00:41:27,290 --> 00:41:28,640
With that apartment in your hand,

911
00:41:28,640 --> 00:41:29,690
those private loan borrowers

912
00:41:29,690 --> 00:41:31,610
wouldn't easily let you off the hook.

913
00:41:31,610 --> 00:41:33,210
You might end up losing the apartment

914
00:41:33,210 --> 00:41:35,610
and paying for that bank loan of 10 million.

915
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:38,240
If they had targeted at your apartment,

916
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:40,330
we wouldn't have been able

917
00:41:40,330 --> 00:41:41,930
to sit and talk to them today.

918
00:41:43,180 --> 00:41:44,320
Thank you, Qiu Hua.

919
00:41:46,010 --> 00:41:48,440
I've always known you're a smart person.

920
00:41:49,090 --> 00:41:51,450
But I didn’t expect you to be so amazing.

921
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:53,880
Even Fang Lihong didn’t think of this point.

922
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:55,160
I'm not that good.

923
00:41:55,780 --> 00:41:57,810
You might still lose your apartment.

924
00:41:57,810 --> 00:42:00,010
But you did help me clear the debts.

925
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:02,270
If I still had that apartment,

926
00:42:02,270 --> 00:42:03,790
as you said,

927
00:42:04,240 --> 00:42:06,770
those people wouldn't have cut me some slack.

928
00:42:06,820 --> 00:42:08,360
As for the 10 million I owe the bank,

929
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:10,520
I wouldn't have been able to pay it back.

930
00:42:10,520 --> 00:42:11,890
All I can say is

931
00:42:13,040 --> 00:42:14,530
thank you.

932
00:42:18,530 --> 00:42:19,860
There's one more thing.

933
00:42:20,100 --> 00:42:22,790
I know this may sound rough.

934
00:42:23,990 --> 00:42:25,650
But I don't think that nanny of yours

935
00:42:25,650 --> 00:42:27,210
is trustworthy.

936
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:29,480
You live alone now.

937
00:42:29,500 --> 00:42:31,630
Is it really necessary to have a nanny?

938
00:42:32,600 --> 00:42:33,640
Lanlan

939
00:42:34,820 --> 00:42:36,330
helped me a lot

940
00:42:36,370 --> 00:42:38,170
when I was in bad shape.

941
00:42:38,940 --> 00:42:40,270
I treat her as my sister.

942
00:42:40,930 --> 00:42:42,930
And she is very diligent.

943
00:42:42,930 --> 00:42:44,260
She's protective of me.

944
00:42:45,050 --> 00:42:46,930
I can't tell her to go away.

945
00:42:46,930 --> 00:42:49,050
I'll feel condemned if I do so.

946
00:42:49,820 --> 00:42:51,780
Anyway, you'd better be wary of her.

947
00:42:51,780 --> 00:42:53,410
Why should I?

948
00:42:53,900 --> 00:42:56,020
Is she gonna sell me out or what?

949
00:42:56,050 --> 00:42:57,360
It's just a little reminder.

950
00:42:57,360 --> 00:42:58,730
I know. I know.
